        <description><![CDATA[
<p>Birchboard now stays out of sight when you share your screen.</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Hidden from screen capture</strong> &mdash; the clipboard panel is excluded from screenshots, screen recordings, and screen-sharing sessions while staying visible to you. On by default; toggle under Settings &rarr; Privacy &rarr; Screen capture.</li>
</ul>
