        <link>https://github.com/birchsport/clipboard-manager/releases/tag/v0.2.10</link>
        <description><![CDATA[
<p>Reorder long-lived pins so they don't sink under newer ones.</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Reorder pinned entries</strong> &mdash; with a pinned row selected, <kbd>&#x2325;&#x2191;</kbd> / <kbd>&#x2325;&#x2193;</kbd> swaps it with the adjacent visible pinned neighbour. Useful when a freshly-pinned row pushes an older pin you actually use further down the list.</li>
</ul>
